{"title":"史光柱诗五首","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":1,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"史光柱诗五首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾飞的龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵啊，不知道什么叫累。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整整一天了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你都在硝烟中跑动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹在这边密集，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边就传出你的声音；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声在那边骤响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边就有你的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声音嘶哑，嘴唇出血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有水壶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怎不润一润喉咙？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵啊，不知道什么叫累。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一个二十四小时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还在烈火中翻滚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在敌人嚎叫的洞穴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有你刺刀的锋刃闪耀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗持续的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有你甩出的手雷轰鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上沾了那么多血污，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有手帕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怎么不把它揩净？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，士兵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是累了，太累了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗间隙你睡了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背依山岩，怀抱钢枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴角溢出了笑容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在做梦吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦见妈妈、未婚妻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是香喷喷的蜜桔甜橙……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睡吧，睡吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这短暂的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽情享受生活的安宁……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦枪声响起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还得冲锋陷阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一条腾飞的龙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子　弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你象一个夺魁的健儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"负着重任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去争夺光荣的桂冠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你象一位复仇的女神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挟着怒火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向一座座山峦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奏响的是生命之曲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱出的是青春之恋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不计较名利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不需要什么奖赏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在粉身碎骨的瞬间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实现了报国的宏愿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木棉花开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木棉花开了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娇艳芬芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记得那一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你抿嘴微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羞赧的脸庞象那红红的木棉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你摘下一朵小花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄声对我说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是咱俩的木棉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我接过小花戴在胸前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此踏上硝烟弥漫的战场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，我戴着勋章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拄着拐杖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归来在鲜花盛开的木棉树下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待，久久的等待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我们没有重逢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地，没有对我说一句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许忘了这朵带血的小花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱情的砝码"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不是不爱你啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的姑娘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边硝烟吞没了秀丽的山岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硝烟下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小花凋零，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草枯黄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不能让嫩草失去翠绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花没有芳香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因而，在祖国与爱情的天平上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才毅然把砝码加到祖国一方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不是不懂感情啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯真的姑娘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边乌云遮住了温暖的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌云里，雷鸣电闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨骤风狂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不能让清晨失去朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野没有金黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因而，我才放弃甜密的幽会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把死亡和痛苦扛在肩上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，美丽善良的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇恨的烈火燃烧着祖国边疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火中，青春奏出人生最强音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命谱写着时代的交响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也是大地的一根琴弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也有青春的串串音符，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因而，我才离开热恋的花丛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赴向烽火与焦土的战场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨树上的那群白鸽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给白衣战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一颗跳动的星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追寻我痛苦的海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用一把锋利的剑砍断我忧郁的目光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一朵轻柔的白云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘进我冰冷的心房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我心灵的天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孕育五彩的霞光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是路边那棵葱茏的白杨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇落了我往日的悲伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是杨树上那群快乐的白鸽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我带来欢笑和歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！我断了源的情泉啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重在大地的缝间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷涌流淌……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}